Despite your protests, the cold woman dumps you into her
mouth like you're just another topping for her salad.\.\. And the conditions
do not improve at all once you are within her jaws.
Her palate caked with a film of stagnating coffee, and
the leftovers of her breakfast strewn amongst filling-laden
teeth, you choke on the stench-ridden saliva that utterly cocoons you.
Her tongue, cloying and slick with white film wrestles you in
with chewed salad mush, tossing you to-and-fro around the
wretched slimy environ of her mouth with absolutely no possibility of resistance.
You're slammed bodily between each tooth, barely avoiding being crushed to paste as the giantess chews her mouthful.\.\. The relentless
tongue shows complete disregard for your well being as your body
bruises from the abuse, and you choke on the mixture of
pulverised salad and saliva infused with her rancid breath.
The never ending abuse and halitosis is so
bad you begin to become desperate for the sweet release of
the giant woman to hurry up and swallow you.
Heralded by a sickening quiver of her gunk-covered throat, your
wish comes true.\.\. The slimy tongue turns to steel,
slamming you and a bolus of well-chewed salad into her palate and mercilessly forcing you
down her throat, past the beat of her cruel heart, and into the active digestion of her waiting stomach.
